description.en: They say a dog is man’s best friend, but for Tsuki that title belongs to Taiyo the monkey! While Tsuki represents the moon with their cool calm and collected demeanor, Taiyo’s fiery and restless energy is a reflection of Taiyo’s home: the sun. This improbable tag team is guaranteed to bring two things to the Tsukiverse: Mission success, and a whole lot of shenanigans along the way.
